isk reflexes point towards something like ALS or maybe another type of motor neuron disease.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031922,0.047971,0.064459,0.079017,0.088959,0.096698,0.10223,0.10216,0.10378,0.1095,0.10048,0.072824],"unified_progress":[0.037934,0.058377,0.073845,0.084367,0.091349,0.098252,0.098547,0.099727,0.098847,0.096173,0.087429,0.075154]},{"section":14,"text":"But wait, let's consider other possibilities.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.11205,0.089949,0.083766,0.075226,0.07625,0.078288,0.080645,0.089376,0.080758,0.055828,0.059532,0.11833],"unified_progress":[0.2036,0.077073,0.063458,0.064404,0.073366,0.073477,0.095767,0.082605,0.079965,0.064896,0.060657,0.060734]},{"section":15,"text":"Could it be something like muscular dystrophy?","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026417,0.052259,0.07196,0.087612,0.094833,0.10189,0.11049,0.1146,0.11504,0.10979,0.077359,0.037748],"unified_progress":[0.035289,0.067254,0.0665,0.094298,0.10496,0.10086,0.10186,0.10729,0.10247,0.093915,0.076752,0.048555]},{"section":16,"text":"Well, muscular dystrophies usually don't cause fasciculations, so that doesn't fit well.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.017193,0.033392,0.048647,0.062222,0.076448,0.093874,0.11149,0.12888,0.1397,0.13826,0.10169,0.048208],"unified_progress":[0.028951,0.054493,0.070777,0.080651,0.093431,0.097991,0.10134,0.10816,0.10672,0.10904,0.089527,0.058924]},{"section":17,"text":"Hmm, what about spinal muscular atrophy?","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.011495,0.03082,0.048074,0.063022,0.077372,0.09563,0.11323,0.1325,0.14398,0.14337,0.10018,0.040335],"unified_progress":[0.025314,0.054324,0.070959,0.082059,0.092203,0.096653,0.1037,0.10801,0.10717,0.11348,0.090138,0.055986]},{"section":18,"text":"That could explain the muscle weakness and atrophy, but it often affects younger people.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.017682,0.029966,0.040088,0.050581,0.062883,0.077687,0.094787,0.10953,0.12491,0.14173,0.14613,0.10402],"unified_progress":[0.031007,0.04974,0.06414,0.074535,0.086104,0.096825,0.099698,0.10563,0.1077,0.10926,0.099838,0.075528]},{"section":19,"text":"And the age doesn't quite match up.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.016783,0.03137,0.043777,0.055393,0.068164,0.084915,0.10356,0.12483,0.14255,0.14699,0.11776,0.063918],"unified_progress":[0.029021,0.052011,0.06657,0.075682,0.087542,0.092404,0.098707,0.10557,0.10708,0.11459,0.10045,0.070382]},{"section":20,"text":"So, I'm leaning back towards ALS, also known as amyotrophic lateral sclerosis.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.016889,0.032127,0.044917,0.057118,0.068731,0.082734,0.096639,0.10969,0.12113,0.12962,0.12719,0.11321],"unified_progress":[0.024732,0.045926,0.059957,0.070508,0.078942,0.087434,0.092324,0.09959,0.10254,0.10902,0.11223,0.1168]},{"section":21,"text":"It's a progressive disease that fits with the symptoms we've got here.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.019786,0.0325,0.039843,0.047433,0.055892,0.065591,0.077221,0.086798,0.10151,0.12525,0.16872,0.17946],"unified_progress":[0.025945,0.041157,0.051625,0.060837,0.069829,0.082345,0.085804,0.095557,0.1037,0.11136,0.12809,0.14376]},{"section":22,"text":"But hold on, let's double-check.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.093715,0.075107,0.07054,0.064244,0.067076,0.072091,0.078099,0.092177,0.088292,0.065083,0.075964,0.15761],"unified_progress":[0.17985,0.068346,0.058654,0.060588,0.069343,0.073152,0.093337,0.086721,0.087248,0.075104,0.072058,0.075596]},{"section":23,"text":"Are there any other conditions that could mimic this?","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.023219,0.049437,0.068767,0.079682,0.086385,0.093715,0.1019,0.10977,0.11506,0.11784,0.097